# Sequence Diagrams

## User Interaction: Facility Search

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant FacilityExplorer
    participant KenyaMap
    participant KenyaData

    User->>FacilityExplorer: Enter search query
    FacilityExplorer->>FacilityExplorer: Update searchQuery state
    FacilityExplorer->>FacilityExplorer: Filter facilities
    FacilityExplorer->>KenyaMap: Pass filtered facilities
    KenyaMap->>KenyaMap: Render map with markers
    KenyaMap-->>User: Display updated map
```

## Map Loading Sequence

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Component
    participant KenyaMap
    participant Leaflet
    participant OpenStreetMap

    Component->>KenyaMap: Mount with facilities
    KenyaMap->>KenyaMap: Set isClient = true
    KenyaMap->>KenyaMap: Initialize map
    KenyaMap->>Leaflet: Create MapContainer
    Leaflet->>OpenStreetMap: Fetch map tiles
    OpenStreetMap-->>Leaflet: Return tiles
    Leaflet-->>KenyaMap: Map ready
    KenyaMap-->>Component: Render with markers
```

## Navigation Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant BrowserRouter
    participant Sidebar
    participant Page

    User->>Sidebar: Click navigation link
    Sidebar->>BrowserRouter: Navigate to route
    BrowserRouter->>BrowserRouter: Update URL
    BrowserRouter->>Page: Load new page component
    Page-->>User: Display new page
```
